    • JNA_OPENVR_LIBRARY_PATH

      public static final String JNA_OPENVR_LIBRARY_PATH
      The system property that specifies an implementation of OpenVR (openvr_api file) to use. This property has to be set at the program launch using -D connector. If this property is not set, the embedded library is loaded.
